# Scoped ignore for docker/atlas/t3.Dockerfile (BuildKit honors <dockerfile>.dockerignore).
# Build context is the repo root; keep it lean. Source + every workspace
# package.json must stay (pnpm --frozen-lockfile needs them); only drop heavy,
# regenerable, or irrelevant paths.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/dist-electron
**/.vite-plus
**/.turbo
.git
.repos
*.log
